t><item>Crosswalked to EpiDoc XML</item></change></revisionDesc></teiHeader><text><body><head lang="en"><date>260/258BC</date>
<placeName cert="high" full="yes">Philadelphia</placeName></head><div type="edition" lang="grc" org="uniform" part="N" sample="complete"><div type="textpart" n="1" org="uniform" part="N" sample="complete"><ab part="N">

    <lb n="1"/>ὑπόμνημα Ζήνωνι 

    <lb n="2"/><del rend="erasure" status="unremarkable"><gap reason="illegible" extent="4" unit="character"/><gap reason="illegible" extent="3" unit="character"/></del> παρὰ Ἡρακλείδου 

    <lb n="3"/>τοῦ συνωριστοῦ. 

    <lb n="4"/>περὶ ὧν ἀπηργασμένοι εἰσὶν 

    <lb n="5"/>Δριμύλος καὶ Διονύσιος 

    <lb n="6"/>παιδίσκην <num value="1">α</num> <note lang="en" anchored="yes" place="not specified">?</note> <del rend="erasure" status="unremarkable"><gap reason="illegible" extent="2" unit="character"/></del> 

    <lb n="7"/>προσχρησάμενος αὐτῆι 

    <lb n="8"/>παρέδωκεν αὐτὴν τῶι 

    <lb n="9"/><app type="BL"><lem resp="cf. 9.314">ὀροφύλακι</lem><rdg><choice><corr>ὁροφύλακι</corr><sic>ορυφυλακι</sic></choice></rdg></app> συνσκευά-

    <lb n="10"/>σαντες αὐτὴν εἴ τί πο-

    <lb n="11"/>τε <choice><corr>εἶχεν</corr><sic>ειχειν</sic></choice>. αὕτη <add place="supralinear">δέ</add> ἐστιν 

    <lb n="12"/><choice><corr>ἐν</corr><sic>εμ</sic></choice> Πηγαῖς παρὰ τῶι <app type="BL"><lem resp="cf. 9.314">ὀροφύλακι</lem><rdg>ὁροφύλακι</rdg></app>. 
<milestone rend="paragraphos" unit="undefined"/>
    <lb n="13"/>ἄλλην <choice><corr>ἐξῆγον</corr><sic>εξηγοσαν</sic></choice> ἐξ Ἀμμώνων. 

    <lb n="14"/>ἀπέδοντο αὐτὴν ἐν Πτολεμαίδι 

    <lb n="15"/>κ<unclear reason="undefined" cert="high">α</unclear>ὶ ιερεα ἤδη τέταρτον <num value=" 1/4 "/> 

    <lb n="16"/>εἰς Ἰόπην καταγήγοχεν 

    <lb n="17"/>καὶ εἰς Αὔρανα ἀπεδήμησεν 

    <lb n="18"/>σῶμα θηλυκὸν ἄγων 

    <lb n="19"/>καὶ ἔλαβεν <expan><ex cert="high">δραχμὰς</ex></expan> <num value="150">ρν</num>. 

    <lb n="20"/><choice><corr>καὶ ἐκεῖθεν</corr><sic>κακειθεν</sic></choice> ἀνακάμπτων 

    <lb n="21"/><app type="editorial"><lem>συνεσκευάσατο</lem><rdg><choice><corr>συνεσκεασατο</corr><sic>συνευκεασατο</sic></choice></rdg></app> τοὺς <app type="BL"><lem resp="1.397">Ἀνα-

    <lb n="22"/>βαταίους</lem><rdg><sic>α</sic> Ναβαταίουσ</rdg></app>. βοῆς δὲ γενομένης 

    <lb n="23"/>ἀπάγεται εἰς φυλακὴν 

    <lb n="24"/>ἡμέρας <num value="7">ζ</num> <choice><corr>ἐν</corr><sic>εμ</sic></choice> πέδαις ὤν. 
</ab></div><div type="textpart" n="2" org="uniform" part="N" sample="complete"><ab part="N">

    <lb n="25"/>καὶ Δριμύλος παιδίσ-

    <lb n="26"/>κην ἠγόραζεν <expan><ex cert="high">δραχμὰς</ex></expan> <num value="300">τ</num>. 

    <lb n="27"/>ἐπ᾽ <choice><corr>ἐξοδίαν</corr><sic>εξοδιαμ</sic></choice> <choice><corr>μὲν</corr><sic>μεγ</sic></choice> γὰρ 

    <lb n="28"/>ἑκάστης ἡμέρας 

    <lb n="29"/>ἐπορεύοντο, καὶ ὠ-

    <lb n="30"/>φελοῦντο λαμπρῶς. 

    <lb n="31"/>καὶ ταῦτα ποιοῦντες 

    <lb n="32"/>οὐκ <choice><corr>εἶχον</corr><sic>ειχοσαν</sic></choice> τὸν 

    <lb n="33"/>νοῦν πρὸς τοῖς κτή-

    <lb n="34"/>νεσιν, ἀλλ᾽ ἢ ὁ μὲν 

    <lb n="35"/>Δριμύλος ἑκάστης 

    <lb n="36"/>ἡμέρας τῆι ἐρωμέ-

    <lb n="37"/>νηι αὐτοῦ ἐθερμαί-

    <lb n="38"/>νετο χαλκία δύο <num value="2"/> 

    <lb n="39"/>ὕδατος· πέπρακεν 

    <lb n="40"/>δὲ καὶ τὴν ὄνον 

    <lb n="41"/>τὴν θήλειαν καὶ 

    <lb n="42"/>τὸν <app type="BL"><lem resp="8.397">ὀνάγριον</lem><rdg><choice><corr>ἄγριον</corr><sic>οναγριον</sic></choice></rdg></app>. 

    <lb n="43"/>καὶ τούτων μάρ-

    <lb n="44"/>τυρες εἰσίν. 

    <lb n="45"/>περὶ δὲ τῶν πλεό-

    <lb n="46"/>νων, <choice><corr>ἐάν</corr><sic>εαμ</sic></choice> με ἐπε-

    <lb n="47"/>ρωτᾶις, εὑρήσεις 

    <lb n="48"/>πᾶσαν τὴν ἀλή-

    <lb n="49"/><choice><corr>θειαν</corr><sic><app type="editorial"><lem>αληθεαν</lem><rdg>αληθειαν</rdg></app></sic></choice>. </ab></div></div><div n="meta.2089" type="description" org="uniform" part="N" sample="complete"><p><rs type="material" cert="high">Papyrus</rs></p></div><div n="meta.2089" type="commentary" subtype="textDate" org="uniform" part="N" sample="complete"><p><date type="textDate" notBefore="-0260" notAfter="-0258">260 - 258 v.Chr.</date></p></div><div n="meta.2089" type="commentary" subtype="general" org="uniform" part="N" sample="complete"><p>Gehört zum Zenon - Archiv. Zur Datierung vgl. BL IX, S. 397. Vgl. Chiron 36, 2006, S. 2-5.</p></div><div n="meta.2089" type="bibliography" subtype="principalEdition" org="uniform" part="N" sample="complete"><listBibl default="NO"><bibl type="publication" subtype="principal" default="NO"><title level="s" type="abbreviated">PSI</title><biblScope type="volume">4</biblScope><biblScope type="numbers">406</biblScope></bibl><bibl type="Trismegistos" default="NO"><biblScope type="numbers">2089</biblScope></bibl><bibl type="DDbDP" default="NO"><series>0238</series>; <biblScope type="volume">4</biblScope>; <biblScope type="numbers">406</biblScope></bibl></listBibl><p>Perseus links: <xref type="Perseus" href="0238;4;406" evaluate="all" from="ROOT" targOrder="Y" to="DITTO">Text in Perseus</xref></p></div><div n="meta.2089" type="bibliography" subtype="corrections" org="uniform" part="N" sample="complete"><head>BL-Einträge nach BL-Konkordanz</head><listBibl default="NO"><bibl type="BL" default="NO"><biblScope type="volume">VIII</biblScope>, S. <biblScope type="pages">397/398</biblScope></bibl><bibl type="BL" default="NO"><biblScope type="volume">IX</biblScope>, S. <biblScope type="pages">314</biblScope></bibl></listBibl></div><div n="meta.2089" type="bibliography" subtype="illustrations" org="uniform" part="N" sample="complete"><p><bibl type="illustration" default="NO">Pap. Flor. XII Suppl., Tav. IV</bibl></p></div><di